#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:14
msgid "Heatmap (kernel density estimation)"
msgstr "Toplotna karta (procena gustine jezgrom)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:15
msgid ""
"Creates a density (heatmap) raster of an input point vector layer using "
"kernel density estimation."
msgstr ""
"Pravi rasterski sloj gustine (toplotnu kartu) od ulaznog tačkastog "
"vektorskog sloja pomoću procene gustine jezgrom."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:18
msgid ""
"The density is calculated based on the number of points in a location, with "
"larger numbers of clustered points resulting in larger values. Heatmaps "
"allow easy identification of *hotspots* and clustering of points."
msgstr ""
"Gustina se računa na osnovu broja tačaka na nekom mestu, pri čemu veći broj "
"grupisanih tačaka daje veće vrednosti. Toplotne karte omogućavaju lako "
"prepoznavanje *žarišta* i grupisanja tačaka."

