#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:44
msgid ""
"Heatmap search radius (or kernel bandwidth) in map units. The radius "
"specifies the distance around a point at which the influence of the point "
"will be felt. Larger values result in greater smoothing, but smaller values "
"may show finer details and variation in point density."
msgstr ""
"Poluprečnik pretrage toplotne karte (ili propusni opseg jezgra) u jedinicama"
" karte. Poluprečnik zadaje rastojanje oko tačke na kojem će se osetiti "
"uticaj te tačke. Veće vrednosti daju veće zaglađivanje, dok manje vrednosti "
"mogu prikazati finije detalje i varijacije u gustini tačaka."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:49
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:332
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:599
