msgstr "**Veličina izlaznog rastera**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:50
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:333
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:442
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:600
msgid "``PIXEL_SIZE``"
msgstr "``PIXEL_SIZE``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:53
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:336
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:603
msgid "Default: 0.1"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: 0.1"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:54
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:337
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:604
msgid "Pixel size of the output raster layer in layer units."
msgstr "Veličina piksela izlaznog rasterskog sloja u jedinicama sloja."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:56
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:339
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:606
msgid ""
"In the GUI, the size can be specified by the number of rows (``Number of "
"rows``) / columns (``Number of columns``) **or** the pixel size( ``Pixel "
"Size X`` / ``Pixel Size Y``). Increasing the number of rows or columns will "
"decrease the cell size and increase the file size of the output raster. The "
"values in ``Rows``, ``Columns``, ``Pixel Size X`` and ``Pixel Size Y`` will "
"be updated simultaneously - doubling the number of rows will double the "
"number of columns, and the cell size will be halved. The extent of the "
"output raster will remain the same (approximately)."
msgstr ""
"U grafičkom okruženju, veličina se može zadati brojem redova (``Broj "
"redova``) / kolona (``Broj kolona``) **ili** veličinom piksela (``Veličina "
"piksela X`` / ``Veličina piksela Y``). Povećanje broja redova ili kolona "
"smanjiće veličinu ćelije i povećati veličinu datoteke izlaznog rastera. "
"Vrednosti u poljima ``Redovi``, ``Kolone``, ``Veličina piksela X`` i "
"``Veličina piksela Y`` ažuriraće se istovremeno - udvostručavanje broja "
"redova udvostručiće broj kolona, a veličina ćelije će se prepoloviti. "
"Obuhvat izlaznog rastera ostaće (približno) isti."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:67
msgid "**Radius from field**"
msgstr "**Poluprečnik iz polja**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:69
