msgstr "[polje tabele: numerički]"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:72
msgid ""
"Sets the search radius for each feature from an attribute field in the input"
" layer."
msgstr ""
"Postavlja poluprečnik pretrage za svaki objekat iz atributskog polja u "
"ulaznom sloju."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:74
msgid "**Weight from field**"
msgstr "**Težina iz polja**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:77
msgid "``WEIGHT_FIELD``"
msgstr "``WEIGHT_FIELD``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:79
msgid ""
"Allows input features to be weighted by an attribute field. This can be used"
" to increase the influence certain features have on the resultant heatmap."
msgstr ""
"Omogućava da ulazni objekti budu ponderisani atributskim poljem. Ovo se može"
" koristiti za povećanje uticaja koji određeni objekti imaju na rezultujuću "
"toplotnu kartu."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:82
msgid "**Kernel shape**"
msgstr "**Oblik jezgra**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:83
msgid "``KERNEL``"
msgstr "``KERNEL``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:84
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:131
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:582
msgid "[enumeration]"
msgstr "[nabrajanje]"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:86
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:133
msgid "Default: *0*"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: *0*"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:87
msgid ""
"Controls the rate at which the influence of a point decreases as the "
"distance from the point increases. Different kernels decay at different "
"rates, so a triweight kernel gives features greater weight for distances "
"closer to the point then the Epanechnikov kernel does. Consequently, "
"triweight results in “sharper” hotspots and Epanechnikov results in "
"“smoother” hotspots."
msgstr ""
"Kontroliše brzinu kojom se uticaj tačke smanjuje kako se rastojanje od tačke"
" povećava. Različita jezgra opadaju različitim brzinama, pa triweight jezgro"
" daje objektima veću težinu na rastojanjima bližim tački nego "
"Epanečnikovljevo jezgro. Zbog toga triweight daje „oštrija“ žarišta, a "
"Epanečnikovljevo „glatkija“ žarišta."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:95
msgid ""
"There are many shapes available (please see the `Wikipedia page "
"<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kernel_(statistics)#Kernel_functions_in_common_use>`_"
" for further information):"
msgstr ""
"Dostupno je mnogo oblika (za više informacija pogledajte `stranicu na "
"Vikipediji "
"<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kernel_(statistics)#Kernel_functions_in_common_use>`_):"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:99
msgid "0 --- Quartic"
msgstr "0 --- Kvartično"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:100
msgid "1 --- Triangular"
msgstr "1 --- Trougaono"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:101
msgid "2 --- Uniform"
msgstr "2 --- Uniformno"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:102
msgid "3 --- Triweight"
msgstr "3 --- Triweight"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:103
msgid "4 --- Epanechnikov"
msgstr "4 --- Epanečnikovljevo"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:105
msgid "**Decay ratio (Triangular kernels only)**"
msgstr "**Odnos opadanja (samo za trougaona jezgra)**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:108
msgid "``DECAY``"
msgstr "``DECAY``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:111
msgid "Default: *0.0*"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: *0.0*"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:112
msgid ""
"Can be used with Triangular kernels to further control how heat from a "
"feature decreases with distance from the feature."
msgstr ""
"Može se koristiti sa trougaonim jezgrima za dodatnu kontrolu načina na koji "
"toplota od objekta opada sa rastojanjem od objekta."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:116
msgid ""
"A value of 0 (=minimum) indicates that the heat will be concentrated in the "
"center of the given radius and completely extinguished at the edge."
msgstr ""
"Vrednost 0 (=minimum) označava da će toplota biti koncentrisana u centru "
"zadatog poluprečnika i potpuno ugašena na ivici."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:119
msgid ""
"A value of 0.5 indicates that pixels at the edge of the radius will be given"
" half the heat as pixels at the center of the search radius."
msgstr ""
"Vrednost 0.5 označava da će pikseli na ivici poluprečnika dobiti upola manje"
" toplote od piksela u centru poluprečnika pretrage."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:122
msgid ""
"A value of 1 means the heat is spread evenly over the whole search radius "
"circle. (This is equivalent to the ‘Uniform’ kernel.)"
msgstr ""
"Vrednost 1 znači da je toplota ravnomerno raspoređena po celom krugu "
"poluprečnika pretrage. (Ovo je ekvivalentno „Uniformnom“ jezgru.)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:125
msgid ""
"A value greater than 1 indicates that the heat is higher towards the edge of"
" the search radius than at the center."
msgstr ""
"Vrednost veća od 1 označava da je toplota veća ka ivici poluprečnika "
"pretrage nego u centru."

