#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:171
msgid ""
"For the following example, we will use the ``airports`` vector point layer "
"from the QGIS sample dataset (see :ref:`label_sampledata`). Another "
"excellent QGIS tutorial on making heatmaps can be found at "
"`http://qgistutorials.com "
"<http://www.qgistutorials.com/en/docs/creating_heatmaps.html>`_."
msgstr ""
"Za sledeći primer koristićemo tačkasti vektorski sloj ``airports`` iz QGIS "
"uzorka podataka (pogledajte :ref:`label_sampledata`). Još jedan odličan QGIS"
" tutorijal o pravljenju toplotnih karata možete pronaći na "
"`http://qgistutorials.com "
"<http://www.qgistutorials.com/en/docs/creating_heatmaps.html>`_."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:177
