#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:392
msgid "Line Density"
msgstr "Gustina linija"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:394
msgid ""
"Calculates for each raster cell, the density measure of linear features "
"within a circular neighbourhood. This measure is obtained by summing all the"
" line segments intersecting the circular neighbourhood and dividing this sum"
" by the area of such neighbourhood. A weighting factor can be applied to the"
" line segments."
msgstr ""
"Za svaku rastersku ćeliju računa meru gustine linijskih objekata unutar "
"kružnog okruženja. Ova mera se dobija sabiranjem svih segmenata linija koji "
"se seku sa kružnim okruženjem i deljenjem tog zbira površinom tog okruženja."
" Na segmente linija može se primeniti faktor ponderisanja."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:400
msgid ""
"This algorithm uses ellipsoid based measurements and respects the current "
":ref:`ellipsoid settings <measurements_ellipsoid>`."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj algoritam koristi merenja zasnovana na elipsoidu i poštuje tekuća "
":ref:`podešavanja elipsoida <measurements_ellipsoid>`."

