#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:519
msgid "TIN Interpolation"
msgstr "TIN interpolacija"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:520
msgid ""
"Generates a Triangulated Irregular Network (TIN) interpolation of a point "
"vector layer."
msgstr ""
"Generiše interpolaciju tačkastog vektorskog sloja metodom nepravilne "
"triangulisane mreže (TIN)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:523
msgid ""
"With the TIN method you can create a surface formed by triangles of nearest "
"neighbor points. To do this, circumcircles around selected sample points are"
" created and their intersections are connected to a network of non "
"overlapping and as compact as possible triangles. The resulting surfaces are"
" not smooth."
msgstr ""
"Metodom TIN možete napraviti površinu sastavljenu od trouglova najbližih "
"susednih tačaka. Za to se oko izabranih uzoračkih tačaka prave opisane "
"kružnice, a njihovi preseci se povezuju u mrežu nepreklapajućih i što je "
"moguće kompaktnijih trouglova. Rezultujuće površine nisu glatke."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/interpolation.rst:530
msgid ""
"The algorithm creates both the raster layer of the interpolated values and "
"the vector line layer with the triangulation boundaries."
msgstr ""
"Algoritam pravi i rasterski sloj interpoliranih vrednosti i vektorski "
"linijski sloj sa granicama triangulacije."

